NFTs, non-fungible tokens.

517
00:39:24,080 --> 00:39:27,440
On a conceptual level the 
tech acts as a sort of generic  

518
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:31,280
database to mediate the exchange of digital stuff.

519
00:39:31,280 --> 00:39:36,480
The most optimistic read on it is a framework for 
a type of computer code that creates so-called  

520
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:41,520
