which is an important concept.

523
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:53,680
Strict uniqueness is a way of 
saying that two different things  

524
00:39:53,680 --> 00:39:58,880
are different things, even if they’re 
different copies of the same thing.

525
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:05,520
My copy of Grey by EL James is strictly unique. 
While millions of copies of the book exist,  

526
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:11,040
this is the only copy that is this copy, 
and this is the only copy that has the  

527
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:15,120
very specific damage of being glued 
shut and thrown into the Bow River.

528
00:40:15,640 --> 00:40:16,640
