529
00:40:16,640 --> 00:40:20,880
It is also strictly scarce. While 
millions of copies of Grey exist,  

530
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:24,080
that’s still a finite number, 
meaning it is possible,  

531
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:28,960
though not immediately practical, 
for the world to run out of copies.

532
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:32,880
NFTs impose a simulacrum of this 
physical scarcity and uniqueness  

533
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:35,360
onto digital objects within their ecosystem.

534
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:37,440
