535
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:42,320
On a technical level a non-fungible token 
is just a token that has a unique serial  

536
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:45,680
number and can’t be subdivided into smaller parts.

537
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:48,800
Two tokens, even two that tokenize the same  

538
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:53,440
conceptual thing, are still strictly 
unique with different serial numbers.

539
00:40:53,440 --> 00:40:56,880
Within the context of Ethereum 
and its clones these tokens are  

540
00:40:56,880 --> 00:41:01,520
