that can contain a payload of code.

541
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:05,120
It’s a box that you can put a micro program into.

542
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:10,000
That micro-program is called a smart contract, a 
name that is so comically full of itself that I  

543
