that has the power to return your tokens,  

1131
01:24:44,720 --> 01:24:51,280
the best you can hope for is denying the scammers 
profit on their incredibly low-cost operation.

1132
01:24:51,280 --> 01:24:54,240
If your business is tricking 
people out of their money  

1133
01:24:54,240 --> 01:24:57,920
you would be a fool if you 
didn’t take the opportunity.

1134
01:24:57,920 --> 01:25:02,560
Not only have participants advertised their 
susceptibility to incoherent promises of  

1135
01:25:02,560 --> 01:25:07,680
future returns, the immutable structure of the 
chain, the persistence of data, and the ease  

1136
01:25:07,680 --> 01:25:14,880
with which that data can be collated, means that 
for scammers it’s extremely easy to find marks.

1137
01:25:14,880 --> 01:25:20,960
Every Discord for a rugpull NFT project is 
a roster of potential victims. The ledger  

1138
01:25:20,960 --> 01:25:25,600
