1156
01:26:38,960 --> 01:26:43,280
Everyone can see what wallets and 
contracts your wallet interacts with  

1157
01:26:43,280 --> 01:26:46,640
based off the long hash addresses like this,  

1158
01:26:46,640 --> 01:26:52,880
but that hash is only implicitly connected to 
your identity based on circumstantial connections.

1159
01:26:52,880 --> 01:26:56,320
Of course a big circumstantial 
connection would be something like  

