possessing more than one, or direct voting  

1758
02:10:06,480 --> 02:10:12,160
power where tokens are spent to cast votes and 
more tokens can be spent to cast more votes.  

1759
02:10:12,160 --> 02:10:15,760
Typically this scrip can be bought and 
